title: 04/13/2021 - Hour 1 - Pete Prisco
itunes:title: 04/13/2021 - Hour 1 - Pete Prisco
description:
Jason Smith and Jason McIntyre are in for Dan and the Danettes, reacting to Jamal Murray going down with a no contact leg injury against the Warriors who were celebrating Steph Curry passing Wilt Chamberlain for most points in franchise history. Senior NFL Columnist for CBS Sports, Pete Prisco joins the guys to discuss whether or not Julian Edelman is a Hall of Famer, what the 49ers are doing with the 3rd pick in the Draft and reports of dysfunction in Philadelphia. Plus, Sam Darnold talks about how tough it was being traded from the Jets.
